  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures. <br /> \rAssuming a departure/destination fuel price ratio of 0.89, the commander decides to optimize fuel tankering by using the following data:</p>\r\r<p>Cruise flight level: FL350 <br /> \rAir distance to be covered: 2650 NM <br /> \rPlanned take-off mass: 190 000 kg (with a minimum prescribed fuel quantity of 30 000 kg that includes a trip fuel of 22 000 kg) <br /> \rMaximum landing mass: 180 000 kg <br /> \rMaximum take-off mass: 205 000 kg <br /> \rMaximum tank capacity: 55 000 kg</p>\r\r<p>The additional fuel quantity will be\u2026</p>",
